data.revised_prompt: Envision an alien military army adorned in futuristic paladin-style armory, poised and ready to maintain peace. Their advanced weapons gleam under the foreign sun, indicating technological superiority. The landscape they stand upon is otherworldly, comprising bizarre structures, intricate formations, and unusual vegetation. The setting captures the alien but palpable sense of control and order. Incorporate the influences from late 19th-century landscape art with a focus on detail, realism, and atmospheric allure executed with oils on canvas, reminiscent of John Schoenherr's descriptive knack but modified to avoid copyright infringement.
